title: [Vornavis, West Road]
description: To the east, a small wooded area crosses the path, and green leaves cling to trees swaying in the breeze.  The road slopes sharply downward for a stretch before turning toward the southwest.  A clump of holly bushes to the north of the path here looks out of place.
